The paper discusses the application of ontologies in identifying requirements patterns in use cases, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of ontologies also involves the management and organization of data, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of ontologies in improving human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
